To finish off this Learning Path, its time for YOU to be creative! For each different section in the song, choose a different beat that youve learned from this Learning Path. Every time one section transitions into a new section, choose a drum fill that youve learned to smoothly bridge the gap between a verse and chorus, for example. The chart that is listed below the video will outline the different sections for you. Have fun!

Related Lessons: Vancouver Pops, U2 Are Led, Two Drumming Princes

artist: Jody Fisher, Baba Elefante, Tilden Webb & Mike Michalkow
Nate Savage, Jordan Leibel, Chelsea Amber
Vinny Valentino, Baron Browne, Joel Rosenblatt
